item.title: The Curse of Bill Cosby & Invasion of the Ratchet
item.description:
We have the homie Ktoe California sit in on the show. We talk about Young Buck selling his music catalog to settle his debt's, and is the woman suing Trey Songz on a money grab? We then go into the rise of ratchet woman in rap and why the change in the statute of limitations will result in a gang of accusations as it relates to Bill Cosby's latest allegation from a former Playboy model in which the alleged incident happened in 1969 and more.
